			<div class="dablink">This article is about the theologian.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Martin_Luther_(disambiguation)" title="Martin Luther (disambiguation)">Martin Luther (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="metadata plainlinks topicon" id="protected-icon" style="position:absolute; z-index:100; right:55px; top:10px;">
